  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/394c6e13b17eb91761de7853eee22cc5.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/394c6e13b17eb91761de7853eee22cc5.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>Interact with bizarre mechanisms, think out of the box to gain your freedom, and discover historical mysteries </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/f6c33ce4608c5d6263ceaf674e953b27.poster.avif?t=1770207122\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/f6c33ce4608c5d6263ceaf674e953b27.webm?t=1770207122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/f6c33ce4608c5d6263ceaf674e953b27.mp4?t=1770207122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/ec0d4127ced236394157ce331918799d.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/ec0d4127ced236394157ce331918799d.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>You will experience a real-life adventure while playing this puzzle game! Lots of intriguing puzzles are waiting for you, ensuring an immersive experience that will keep you engaged for hours </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/7e97b2b4b8e5706b2f0220fa7b0ea94d.avif?t=1770207122\" width=614 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/65f8444bd7166f1ba752b34d32d677d9.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/65f8444bd7166f1ba752b34d32d677d9.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>Examine several mechanisms to unlock each box and gain your freedom </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/c5a0da0da35b19bd6b411d8659446354.poster.avif?t=1770207122\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/c5a0da0da35b19bd6b411d8659446354.webm?t=1770207122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/c5a0da0da35b19bd6b411d8659446354.mp4?t=1770207122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/5b890bfd70dce3cef1596e57d367e61b.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/5b890bfd70dce3cef1596e57d367e61b.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>For an unforgettable experience, immerse yourself in the adventure by playing the game with your headphones on! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/ed0cd39d97d142c60e6fec64f76172e8.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/ed0cd39d97d142c60e6fec64f76172e8.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>Click the bulb button to get hints that will help you through the game, or get in touch with the developer if you seriously get stuck ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/f190ac9fb8841e5215327e0001f69f6d.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/f190ac9fb8841e5215327e0001f69f6d.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>This is an extra challenge that will keep your brain busy for days. Open the letter inside the Enigmas Box and crack a new riddle daily. How far can you go? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/a1ef435bf16d1f717e765ef3b9afb87e.poster.avif?t=1770207122\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/a1ef435bf16d1f717e765ef3b9afb87e.webm?t=1770207122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/a1ef435bf16d1f717e765ef3b9afb87e.mp4?t=1770207122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/4157dbc5c37eb63c9439ef067be3eed1.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/4157dbc5c37eb63c9439ef067be3eed1.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span>Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*<strong>The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1770207122\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1770207122 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong> here. I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing everything myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam; your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
